title_bed_bats_review: Boutique hotel in Gaibandha District · 1 bedroom · 1 bed · 1 private bath
listing_description: Enjoy a luxurious experience when you stay at this special place in Gaibandha. SKS Inn is the largest multi-cuisine 4-Star Resort in North Bengal, Bangladesh. Upgraded rooms include Lake views, minibars, and access to a Restaurant with complimentary breakfast and all-day refreshments. Suites add living rooms and kitchens. There's a refined international restaurant and a brasserie serving afternoon tea, as well as a Cafe. Amenities include a fitness room, meeting rooms, banquet and parking.
